			<p>
				Here's a bit more <a href='/notes/about-these-notes'>about these notes</a> to explain how they work.
			</p>
			<h2>Recently updated</h2>
			<ol class="list-disc">		{allPosts.map(blogPostEntry => (
				<li>
				  <a href={`/notes/${blogPostEntry.slug}`}>{blogPostEntry.data.title}</a>

